Definition: positioning with respect to a reference system or determining your bearings physically or intellectually
Example: noticed the bee's momentary orienting pause before heading back to the hive; an orienting program for new employees
Synonyms: DISORIENTING, orientating, ORIENTED, positioning, with, respect, to, a, reference, system, or, determining, your, bearings, physically, intellectually, noticed, the, bee, s, momentary, orienting, pause, before, heading, back, hive, an, program, for, new, employees
Category: adj.all
